snippet.title: SOMOY TV
snippet.description:
#SomoyTV, From our starting day to till now, we are successfully ensuring to bring justice to injustice, give voice to the voiceless, and put light to every unfairness which causes degradation to our society. We never compromise with authentic news and never promote yellow journalism.
Confused about so many haphazard news which are based on illogical facts? Our news are collected from reliable sources and international news are collected from the Reuters, APTN, SNTV. Subscribe to our YouTube channel now if you wanted to be on the right path.

Subscribe to our Channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCxHoBXkY88Tb8z1Ssj6CWsQ
